MA_4_Imputation

This script contains the missing data analysis and the preparation of the MAR and two MNAR imputation models.

Load Packages and Data

library(tidyverse)
library(mice)
library(ggmice)

df_final <- readRDS("df_final.RData")
demo_data <- readRDS("demo_data.RData")

Missing Data Analysis

Missing Data Pattern

na_ind <- data.frame(!is.na(df_final)) + 0
sum(!complete.cases(df_final))/length(df_final$patient)
## [1] 0.4341085

Missing Data Mechanisms

Compare Missing Post to Not-Missing Post BDI

df_plot <- df_final %>% 
  mutate(BDI_missing = ifelse(is.na(df_final$BDI_post),
                              "Missing", "Not Missing"))

df_long <- df_plot %>%
  pivot_longer(cols = c(mean_pos_T5, mean_neg_T5, rmssd_pos_T5, rmssd_neg_T5,
                        mean_pos_T55, mean_neg_T55, rmssd_pos_T55, rmssd_neg_T55),
               names_to = "Variable",
               values_to = "Value")

ggplot(df_long, aes(x = BDI_missing, y = Value)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  facet_wrap(~Variable, scales = "free") +
  labs(x = "Post BDI Missingness", y = "Value",
       title = "Comparison of Variables by BDI_post Missingness")

Imputation Model

Merge Data

df_imp <- merge(demo_data,  df_final, 
                by = "patient")

Prepare Imputation

method_vec <- make.method(df_imp)

# Passive Imputation
method_vec["delta_BDI"] <- "~I(BDI_post - BDI_prae)"

print(method_vec)

##             delta_rmssd_neg 
##                          ""
pred_mat <- quickpred(df_imp, exclude = c("patient", "delta_BDI", 
                                          "delta_mean_pos", "delta_mean_neg",
                                          "delta_rmssd_pos", "delta_rmssd_neg"))

plot_pred(pred_mat, label = F, rotate = T)

MAR Imputation Model

imp_MAR_test <- futuremice(df_imp,
                           method = method_vec,
                           predictorMatrix = pred_mat,
                           m = 5, maxit = 30,
                           parallelseed = 2025)

MNAR Imputation Models

MNAR1

Post processing command

We will add an offset of 5 (i.e. 0.5 SD) to each missing BDI value. To ensure realistic imputations, we will add less to participants with imputed values close to the maximum value of 63.

post1 <- make.post(df_imp)

post1["BDI_prae"] <- "imp[[j]][,i] <- ifelse(imp[[j]][,i] < 63,
imp[[j]][,i] + pmin(5, 63 - imp[[j]][,i]), imp[[j]][,i])"

post1["BDI_post"] <- "imp[[j]][,i] <- ifelse(imp[[j]][,i] < 63,
imp[[j]][,i] + pmin(5, 63 - imp[[j]][,i]), imp[[j]][,i])"
imp_MNAR1_test <- futuremice(df_imp,
                             method = method_vec,
                             predictorMatrix = pred_mat,
                             post = post1,
                             m = 5, maxit = 30,
                             parallelseed = 2025)

MNAR2

Post processing command

post2 <- make.post(df_imp)

post2["BDI_prae"] <- "imp[[j]][,i] <- ifelse(imp[[j]][,i] > 0,
imp[[j]][,i] - pmin(5, imp[[j]][,i]), imp[[j]][,i])"

post2["BDI_post"] <- "imp[[j]][,i] <- ifelse(imp[[j]][,i] > 0,
imp[[j]][,i] - pmin(5, imp[[j]][,i]), imp[[j]][,i])"
imp_MNAR2_test <- futuremice(df_imp,
                             method = method_vec,
                             predictorMatrix = pred_mat,
                             post = post2,
                             m = 5, maxit = 30,
                             parallelseed = 2025)

Descriptive results

Depression in the MAR imputed datasets

BDI pre-therapy

imp_MAR <- readRDS("imp_MAR.RData")
MAR_mean_prae <- with(imp_MAR, mean(BDI_prae))
mean(unlist(MAR_mean_prae$analyses))
## [1] 22.69285
MAR_sd_prae <- with(imp_MAR, sd(BDI_prae))
mean(unlist(MAR_sd_prae$analyses))
## [1] 9.735997

BDI post-therapy

MAR_mean_post <- with(imp_MAR, mean(BDI_post))
mean(unlist(MAR_mean_post$analyses))
## [1] 11.8831
MAR_sd_post <- with(imp_MAR, sd(BDI_post))
mean(unlist(MAR_sd_post$analyses))
## [1] 9.987139

BDI difference score

MAR_mean_delta <- with(imp_MAR, mean(delta_BDI))
mean(unlist(MAR_mean_delta$analyses))
## [1] -10.80975
MAR_sd_delta <- with(imp_MAR, sd(delta_BDI))
mean(unlist(MAR_sd_delta$analyses))
## [1] 12.26828
